%^BOLD%^-=%^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^Illusion Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Casters with access to this domain have the powerful 
force of perception on their side.  They are able to 
protect themselves in various ways by throwing off 
those who try to see them, and they are likewise able 
to bring forth figments to torment others.

The illusion domain contains the following spells:
Displacement (3rd), Screen (6th), and Phantasmal Killer (8th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: The Faceless One

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     